sectionText: This is a self contained 3 credit hour online course. Students in the online DL course do not register for a discussion section. Video lectures, course materials, and a discussion board will be made available online through Compass 2g.  Optional face-to-face Supplementary Instruction sessions will also be available to all students. .Students are expected to complete online assignments as outlined in the course syllabus.  This section has one or more proctored exams which will be administered in-person; an online option for taking exams is available and may carry additional fees.
